ata or native-image config files, per repository rules. The reporter-requested Connector `getProperty` / `setProperty` path is already covered by the existing `ConnectorProtocolIntrospectionTest`.\n\nTests were not run, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a2c21690d238812016a353aa7cbe08195ab2aa0d54682e955\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 530, "output": 483, "cacheRead": 18944, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 19957, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781873313793, "responseId": "resp_0a2c21690d238812016a353aa25a5081958d17571b8a86d719"}, "toolResults": []}
